Text: It's a cam....why not just tell everybody?
dtsm> Can you read? It says TS in the title...
Is HDTS short for crap video?

hdts is short for high definition telesync. which means it was a cam shot with an hd camcorder, and the audio is audio spliced in from a direct audio track, instead of recorded with a microphone. still a cam, but with better audio. Until a TC (telecine) copy comes out, or an r5/r6 release, this is likely the best you'll see until yify group gets their hands on an actual bluray and posts it.
